txt_content:
玩家运行如下函数，无法使两只僵尸互相发起攻击。
版本：1.15.2summon minecraft:zombie ~ ~ ~ {Tags:["A"]}
summon minecraft:zombie ~ ~ ~ {Tags:["B"]}
execute as @e[tag=A] at @s run summon minecraft:snowball ~ ~2 ~ {Tags:["snow_ball"]}
execute as @e[tag=snow_ball] run data modify entity @s owner.L set from entity @e[limit=1,tag=B] UUIDLeast
execute as @e[tag=snow_ball] run data modify entity @s owner.M set from entity @e[limit=1,tag=B] UUIDMost
execute as @e[tag=B] at @s run summon minecraft:snowball ~ ~2 ~ {Tags:["snow_ball"]}
execute as @e[tag=snow_ball] run data modify entity @s owner.L set from entity @e[limit=1,tag=A] UUIDLeast
execute as @e[tag=snow_ball] run data modify entity @s owner.M set from entity @e[limit=1,tag=A] UUIDMost复制代码

